  <section class="content-section bg-dark">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2 class="section-title">How We Work</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">Three simple steps to get your safe issue resolved professionally.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="how-it-works-grid">
        <div class="hiw-step">
          <div class="hiw-number">01</div>
          <h3>Call or Message</h3>
          <p>Call <a href="tel:07809887883" style="color:var(--color-accent)">07809 887 883</a> or <a href="https://wa.me/447809887883" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color:var(--color-accent)">WhatsApp</a>. Tell William about your safe — make, model, the problem, and your location. He'll advise on the best approach.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hiw-step">
          <div class="hiw-number">02</div>
          <h3>We Arrange a Visit</h3>
          <p>An appointment is arranged at a time that suits you. William travels to your location — home or business, anywhere in the UK. A written quote is provided before work begins.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hiw-step">
          <div class="hiw-number">03</div>
          <h3>Problem Solved</h3>
          <p>Non-destructive opening is always tried first. Work is completed on site in most cases. Your safe is left fully functional and secure. No hidden charges.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- QUOTE FORM -->
  <section class="content-section bg-white" id="get-quote">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="quote-cta-section">
        <h2 class="section-title">Get a Quote for Safe Engineering</h2>
        <p class="quote-cta-text">
          Get in touch with your safe details and William will provide a clear, no-obligation quote.
